### Pengujian Titik Akhir API Manajemen Kontak (Customer & Vendor)
### PENTING: Ganti {{token}} dengan token JWT dari hasil login di test_auth.http
### companyId diambil otomatis dari JWT (tidak perlu diisi di body)

# 1. Membuat Kontak Baru — Tipe CUSTOMER
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN, KASIR
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJwYW5qYW5na2FzYUBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzMyOTY0OTQsImV4cCI6MTc3MzM4Mjg5NH0.w7nD0k8LFevj1IJ1GHR3eHXca1fWQ5yQNjjkk8XXDDQ

{
  "type": "CUSTOMER",
  "name": "CV Pelanggan Setia",
  "phone": "081234567890",
  "email": "pelanggan@setia.com"
}

###

# 2. Membuat Kontak Baru — Tipe VENDOR
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN, KASIR
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJwYW5qYW5na2FzYUBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzMyOTY0OTQsImV4cCI6MTc3MzM4Mjg5NH0.w7nD0k8LFevj1IJ1GHR3eHXca1fWQ5yQNjjkk8XXDDQ

{
  "type": "VENDOR",
  "name": "PT Supplier Utama",
  "phone": "089876543210",
  "email": "supplier@utama.com"
}

###

# 3. Melihat Daftar Kontak Perusahaan
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN, KASIR
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJwYW5qYW5na2FzYUBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzMyOTY0OTQsImV4cCI6MTc3MzM4Mjg5NH0.w7nD0k8LFevj1IJ1GHR3eHXca1fWQ5yQNjjkk8XXDDQ

###

# 4. Melihat Detail Kontak Spesifik (Untuk Contact Detail Drawer)
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN, KASIR
# PENTING: Ganti {{contactId}} dengan UUID kontak dari response request #1 atau #2
# Security: endpoint ini memvalidasi bahwa kontak milik perusahaan user yang login
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts/5aac0ee6-8457-4848-a813-d8488540fc7d
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJwYW5qYW5na2FzYUBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzMyOTY0OTQsImV4cCI6MTc3MzM4Mjg5NH0.w7nD0k8LFevj1IJ1GHR3eHXca1fWQ5yQNjjkk8XXDDQ

###

# 5. Menghapus Kontak (Delete Kontak)
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN, KASIR
# PENTING: 
#   - Ganti {{contactId}} dengan UUID kontak yang ingin dihapus
#   - Penghapusan akan ditolak (400 Bad Request) jika kontak sudah memiliki invoice/tagihan
#   - Jika berhasil: soft delete (data di-mark dengan deletedAt, bukan hard delete)
# TESTING SCENARIOS:
#   - Scenario 1: Hapus kontak baru yang belum punya invoice → SUCCESS (200)
#   - Scenario 2: Hapus kontak yang sudah punya invoice → FAILED (400 with validation error)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts/5aac0ee6-8457-4848-a813-d8488540fc7d
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJwYW5qYW5na2FzYUBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzMyOTY0OTQsImV4cCI6MTc3MzM4Mjg5NH0.w7nD0k8LFevj1IJ1GHR3eHXca1fWQ5yQNjjkk8XXDDQ
